rows.label: qst104003_msg001
rows.name:
Ugh... It's you... I'm alright.
It's not a serious injury.

rows.label: qst104003_msg002
rows.name:
But the young lady was
abducted by ruffians...!

rows.label: qst104003_msg003
rows.name:
I don't know how it leaked, but they
knew the young lady's identity.

rows.label: qst104003_msg005
rows.name:
It's shameful, but we were too
weak... We couldn't protect her.

rows.label: qst104003_msg006
rows.name:
Please, could you
rescue the young lady?

rows.label: qst104003_msg008
rows.name:
I hear there's a place nearby called
the Forbidden Zone Garrison.

rows.label: qst104003_msg009
rows.name: The enemy has likely fled there.

rows.label: qst104003_msg010
rows.name:
I'm counting on you to
save the young lady.

rows.label: qst104003_msg101
rows.name:
The ruffians likely fled
to a place called the
Forbidden Zone Garrison.

rows.label: qst104003_msg102
rows.name: I'm sorry, but I'm in your debt...
